was witnessed
fleeing the scene.

72
00:05:18,291 --> 00:05:20,083
All righty.

73
00:05:20,166 --> 00:05:21,250
What's wrong?

74
00:05:21,333 --> 00:05:24,375
Well um, we didn't
pay anyone for our food.

75
00:05:25,416 --> 00:05:27,791
That rube inside was
about to pay his tab

76
