When you see it,
you say a prayer.

104
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:51,208
Everyone says that's
how your wish is granted.

105
00:06:51,291 --> 00:06:53,125
So you don't believe in it?

106
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:55,166
A Maria statue suddenly
appearing in the middle

107
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:58,041
of nowhere and wishes
being granted?

108
00:06:58,125 --> 00:06:59,916
I'm young but I'm not stupid.

109
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:04,083
Those stories sound like dreams;
like a whole buncha nonsense.

110
00:07:15,708 --> 00:07:19,500
The real world is a lot less
forgiving than that.

111
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:24,875
It's fine, take it.

112
00:07:29,041 --> 00:07:31,583
You didn't have to
but thanks, Rita.

113
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:41,250
Curious about that?

114
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:43,791
Because I happen
to work there.

115
00:07:43,875 --> 00:07:46,125
Come by anytime
and I'll get you in.

116
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:47,750
Are you sure?

117
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,083
It's a promise.

118
00:07:51,166 --> 00:07:52,541
So come.

119
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,250
Oh, shoot.

120
00:07:56,333 --> 00:07:57,791
Gotta go.

121
00:07:57,875 --> 00:07:58,458
Okay.

122
00:07:58,541 --> 00:08:00,083
See ya.

123
00:08:12,708 --> 00:08:15,750
