Don't get up!

126
00:08:27,416 --> 00:08:29,041
You do not look down at me!

127
00:08:29,125 --> 00:08:31,541
I told you to keep
an eye on that girl!

128
00:08:31,625 --> 00:08:32,666
What's your deal?

129
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:34,041
She came back, didn't she?

130
00:08:34,125 --> 00:08:36,208
Don't talk back
to me, you fool!

131
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,791
Why didn't you come?

132
00:08:51,875 --> 00:08:52,583
Why bother?

133
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:54,041
You came right back here.

134
00:08:54,125 --> 00:08:55,375
Dang it Gino!

135
00:08:55,458 --> 00:08:57,250
Do what I want you to do now!

136
00:08:57,333 --> 00:09:00,125
Otherwise, I'm
leaving for real!

137
00:09:10,125 --> 00:09:11,291
Did I wake you?

138
00:09:19,541 --> 00:09:20,666
You okay?

139
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:26,541
You have anyone you like?

140
00:09:26,625 --> 00:09:28,791
Because, that's
the problem I have.

141
00:09:28,875 --> 00:09:30,625
His name's Gino.

142
00:09:30,708 --> 00:09:35,250
We're always together and we
have been ever since I was born.

143
00:09:35,333 --> 00:09:39,041
You see, my parents abandoned
me outside of that tent.

144
00:09:39,125 --> 00:09:42,500
The first thing I ever
remember seeing was Gino.

145
00:09:42,583 --> 00:09:44,791
I'm always looking at him.

146
00:09:44,875 --> 00:09:48,666
But then,
he never looks at me.

147
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:50,708
So I've tried to make
him jealous by talking

148
00:09:50,791 --> 00:09:55,833
to a whole bunch of men but
he still doesn't look at me.

149
00:09:55,916 --> 00:10:00,291
Even when I run away like this,
he won't come after me.

150
00:10:00,375 --> 00:10:04,958
My heart aches like it's
all tangled up in my chest.

151
00:10:21,416 --> 00:10:23,583
Good morning!

152
00:10:26,791 --> 00:10:29,083
Good morning!

153
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,750
Good morning!

154
