156
00:10:45,583 --> 00:10:48,083
Don't you go making eyes
at my Rita anymore!

157
00:10:48,166 --> 00:10:50,250
Or else, my fist is
gonna meet your face!

158
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:50,958
Whoa!

159
00:10:51,041 --> 00:10:52,375
Look, I'm a girl!

160
00:10:52,458 --> 00:10:53,750
I'll bet you are!

161
00:10:53,833 --> 00:10:57,000
And that just
proves my-- Huh?

162
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:06,208
Listen, could you
come with me for a bit?

163
00:11:06,291 --> 00:11:07,083
Huh?

164
00:11:07,166 --> 00:11:08,833
Just come on!

165
00:11:17,625 --> 00:11:18,708
Fine lady, right?

166
00:11:18,791 --> 00:11:20,166
Name's Natália.

167
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:21,875
She's Gino's girlfriend.

168
00:11:21,958 --> 00:11:24,958
Oh yeah, and he
just knocked her up.

169
00:11:25,041 --> 00:11:26,625
And now you know what's what.

170
00:11:26,708 --> 00:11:29,333
Go on, you can order
anything you like.

171
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,166
No one can make Rita happy.

172
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:35,625
