176
00:11:39,791 --> 00:11:40,291
Hey!

177
00:11:40,375 --> 00:11:41,375
You get it?

178
00:11:41,458 --> 00:11:43,916
I'm askin' you
to shill for me.

179
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:47,666
