You're okay.

186
00:12:33,791 --> 00:12:34,375
Stop it!

187
00:12:34,458 --> 00:12:36,041
Don't touch me!

188
00:12:44,375 --> 00:12:45,541
Move it, ya little snot!

189
00:12:45,625 --> 00:12:46,958
Lemme go!

190
00:12:47,041 --> 00:12:48,916
You some kinda thief,
creepin' around like a roach?

191
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:49,541
No!

192
00:12:49,625 --> 00:12:50,958
I am not a thief!

193
00:12:51,041 --> 00:12:51,708
Hana!

194
00:12:51,791 --> 00:12:52,666
Rita!

195
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,500
Take that,
you nasty, filthy--!

196
00:13:02,250 --> 00:13:03,250
What's wrong?

197
