Rita come out yet?

204
00:13:36,708 --> 00:13:37,708
Huh-uh.

205
00:13:37,791 --> 00:13:39,291
Oh, I see.

206
00:13:39,375 --> 00:13:41,250
Thank you very much.

207
00:13:45,833 --> 00:13:46,708
No, wait.

208
00:13:46,791 --> 00:13:49,708
You're Gino, aren't you?

209
00:13:49,791 --> 00:13:51,000
I'm Hana.

210
00:13:51,083 --> 00:13:54,000
