211
00:13:54,083 --> 00:13:57,000
She's in an awful lot of pain.

212
00:13:57,083 --> 00:13:58,208
How come?

213
00:13:58,291 --> 00:14:03,458
It's because of the way
she feels about you.

214
00:14:03,541 --> 00:14:06,958
So please, if you could,
give her a closer look.

215
00:14:07,041 --> 00:14:09,041
