ahead of her, right?

232
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:47,291
She'll meet all sorts of guys,
and eventually find someone

233
00:14:47,375 --> 00:14:48,916
who's right for her.

234
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,958
She'll be a fine
woman someday.

235
00:15:15,458 --> 00:15:17,375
Rita.

236
00:15:17,458 --> 00:15:20,541
I didn't know
where else I could go.

237
00:15:23,833 --> 00:15:24,875
I'm sorry.

238
00:15:24,958 --> 00:15:28,583
There's something
wrong with me.

239
00:15:31,291 --> 00:15:35,000
Are you leaving?

240
00:15:35,083 --> 00:15:36,916
I'll come with you.

241
00:15:45,625 --> 00:15:46,541
Mm-hm.

242
00:15:46,625 --> 00:15:47,791
It's Masão's.

243
00:15:47,875 --> 00:15:49,500
Rock-paper-scissors!

244
00:15:49,583 --> 00:15:51,625
One, two, three!

245
00:15:51,708 --> 00:15:53,125
Get on.

246
00:15:53,208 --> 00:15:54,291
Hurry up.

247
00:15:57,458 --> 00:15:58,500
Ready?

248
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:00,125
Yup.

249
00:16:03,041 --> 00:16:03,875
Easy, Hana!

250
00:16:03,958 --> 00:16:05,041
Whoa!

251
00:16:44,083 --> 00:16:45,500
What are you guys doing?

252
00:16:45,583 --> 00:16:47,833
