254
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:51,375
Some damn idiot ran off
with the other one's head.

255
00:16:51,458 --> 00:16:53,250
Buncha savages around here.

256
00:16:53,333 --> 00:16:55,666
Anyway, we swapped
it out for a new one.

257
00:17:00,083 --> 00:17:05,083
