I'm finally a grownup.

265
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:15,666
Would you two get to work?

266
00:18:25,833 --> 00:18:26,333
Rita!

267
00:18:26,416 --> 00:18:27,166
Gino!

268
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,625
