269
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:35,750
Gino Costa and Rita Ozzetti!

270
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:53,916
Hop to, everybody!

271
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,791
We're outta here tomorrow!

272
00:20:06,125 --> 00:20:08,166
Awesome show as always, Gino.

273
00:20:21,250 --> 00:20:22,875
I'm okay now.

274
00:20:25,458 --> 00:20:27,291
Hey.

275
00:20:27,375 --> 00:20:29,333
You look great out there.

276
00:20:31,041 --> 00:20:32,666
Thank you, Hana.

